flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    Ingest[Ingestion Service<br/>validate / dedupe / route]
    Prefs[(Preferences Store)]
    Templates[(Template Store)]
    Idem[(Idempotency Cache<br/>in-memory KV, 24h TTL)]
    PushQ[(Push Queue)]
    EmailQ[(Email Queue)]
    SMSQ[(SMS Queue)]
    PushW[APNs / FCM Workers]
    EmailW[SES Workers]
    SMSW[Twilio Workers]
    Status[(Status Store + DLQ)]

    Client -->|notify request| Ingest
    Ingest -->|lookup| Prefs
    Ingest -->|render| Templates
    Ingest <-->|dedup check| Idem
    Ingest -->|route| PushQ
    Ingest -->|route| EmailQ
    Ingest -->|route| SMSQ
    PushQ --> PushW
    EmailQ --> EmailW
    SMSQ --> SMSW
    PushW -.->|ack / fail| Status
    EmailW -.->|ack / fail| Status
    SMSW -.->|ack / fail| Status
    Status -.->|retry via DLQ| PushQ

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class Ingest,PushW,EmailW,SMSW service
    class Prefs,Templates,Idem,PushQ,EmailQ,SMSQ,Status store
